Members of the political elite such as presidential candidate Marcel Claude use social media to spread their message, in this case in favor of student movements via Twitter.
Marcel Claude's lecture given at the Universidad del Mar was published in Chile Movilizado as an event of mobilization.
Chile Movilizado aims to achieve full coverage of student protests in the future.
